    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 21</em>, <em>Ultimate Combat pg. 132</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 6 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 1 lb.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d3 (small), 1d4 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> 20 ft.; <strong>Type</strong> S or P; <strong>Special</strong> disarm, grapple, monk, reach</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Two-Handed; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Flails; Monk</p><h3>Description</h3><p>This weapon consists of a foot-long double-edged blade, with another smaller, curved hook-blade sticking out the side like a rooster's spur. The blade is strung to a large iron hoop with a 10-foot length of rope. The blade can be used as an off-handed melee weapon or thrown like a dagger, while the rope and circlet can be whipped around and swung at opponents as a bludgeoning reach weapon.</p>"
